            After we met with Eric a few days before the wedding Eric texted me with a wonderful idea. He and I arranged a surprise recorded toast from Jeff's parents.
            It made the day so special for us. Plus, Jeff's parents felt included even from a distance.
        </em>
    </p>
    <p>
        <em>
            We really appreciated the support and guidance in designing the sound of our wedding.
        </em>
    </p>
    <p>
        <em>
            We also really appreciated Eric and Steve's professional, friendly personalities. They were the perfect choice for us.
        </em>
    </p>
    <p>
        <em>
            Our wedding was an upscale family event in a historic venue. Having Eric and Steve guide us all through the day was so lovely.
            Even family members who "don't dance" got out on the dance floor and had a fun time.
